{"tid":1601002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（香港人記仇系列）10.1 的士掛國旗","createTime":"2019-09-29T00:13:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T02:47:07.000Z","uid":20689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f01db258fb60a7d396ad0d74c019d27413048555","tid":1601002,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:13:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人就最記仇 你今日為左800蚊出賣香港人，我要你以為每日連800蚊都賺唔到！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【逆權運動】的總出價$800號召的士10.1掛國旗遊行 司機狂報名半個鐘已爆額<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1600634\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1600634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n適合：和理非、得閒無屎屙既連登仔<br />\n<br />\n行動：出去抄曬佢地車牌 再放上黎連登 我會幫佢地做整合list <br />\n<br />\n目標：建立「奶共」的士司機表 長遠罷坐奶共司機車<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奶共是有後果，奶共前請先三思。"},{"pid":"57f7ebbf810ba15d289d84be34814cb9c5413b06","tid":1601002,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:16:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n買完新iphone 想測試下長鏡頭質素？<br />\n<br />\n10.1 出黎影低d的士佢啦！<br />\n<br />\n我要瘋狂影的士！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a63d3eb41e6033c4bdb2a01c168dea5ed022e5","tid":1601002,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>長鏡 車牌 運輸署</strong></span>"},{"pid":"700dcbe6eaa3585466ca9f9f4ee5fefb1b9a80c4","tid":1601002,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>長鏡 車牌 運輸署</strong></span>"},{"pid":"a135f262114c4948ee28311dab0db0620ab4f871","tid":1601002,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T00:48:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>長鏡 車牌 運輸署</strong></span>"},{"pid"